rabo karabekian is a fictional character and the narrator and protagonist of the 1987 novel bluebeard by american author kurt vonnegut , jr.   in vonnegut 's fiction he is an abstract expressionist artist who appears first in the 1973 novel breakfast of champions as the artist of the $ 50,000 painting the temptation of saint anthony .

fictional characters : rabo karabekian , a minor character in " breakfast of champions " , is the focus of his 1987 novel " bluebeard "

